BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Zk5qT651wCWy01Ts3DOwR
SUMMARY:Food and Cooking Through Science
DTSTAMP:20260315T234229Z
DTSTART:20260317T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Gain a deeper insight into what’s going on when you cook and ba
	ke! Whether you are a home cook or a professional\, you can become a much 
	better cook by learning the science of food and cooking. You'll fall in lo
	ve with cooking\, as well as the beauty of the amazing world we live in.\n
	\nFocus on understanding the fascinating field of food science through a c
	ombination of fun and fascinating lectures and demos. Learn to make better
	 choices about cooking methods and techniques\, and how to produce better 
	finished products more easily and consistently.\n\nElevate your knowledge 
	about nutrition\, how food works\, sustainability issues\, and the chemist
	ry of cooking and baking. Develop modern techniques using scientific princ
	iples.\n\nLearn many fundamental concepts and apply them to real-world coo
	king and baking.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/food-and
	-cooking-through-science/17755027/2026-03-16T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Eve
	nts
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/food-and-cooking-through-
	science/17755027/2026-03-16T00
LOCATION:Seattle Central College Continuing Education\, 1701 Broadway\, Sea
	ttle\, WA
