DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center (1.2 miles NW)\n\nPacific Northwest Ballet perfo
	rms Firebird about a beautiful\, mythical bird that comes to the aid of tw
	o lovers after a sorcerer casts a cruel spell\, plus two other works at Mc
