	country\, featuring over 200 wineries\, 70 restaurants\, and a host of oth
	er exciting events and activities.\\*Please note\\* - One ticket is valid 
	for both days.This event is ages 21\\+ with valid ID. Please note vertical
	 IDs are not accepted. Patrons must have a valid\, horizontal ID. If you d
	o not have a horizontal ID\, a passport can be used as a substitute.   The
	re are no refunds or exchanges -- all sales are final.\n\nhttps://seatoday
	.6amcity.com/events/#/details/the-grand-tasting-taste-washington-2-day-tic
